{"tid":1523571,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"全世界同我上twitter推爆黑警入太子車廂既post!!","createTime":"2019-08-31T15:57:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T16:42:58.000Z","uid":48777,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"c795411d3c9e803bb1c3e53a35b58a9386b084a3","tid":1523571,"uid":48777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:57:08.000Z","msg":"快撚啲幫手推爆今日黑警入太子車廂無差別攻擊無辜市民！<br />\n<br />\n要同全世界講香港已進入人道危機！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/fight4hongkong/status/1167820567015092225?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ffight4hongkong%2Fstatus%2F1167820567015092225%3Fs%3D21&d=30ZlKbyCH33W3wkrfz60C29Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=e4396ed5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ffight4hongkong%2Fstatus%2F1167820567015092225%3Fs%3D21&h=689a1a5c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/fight4hongkong/status/1167820567015092225?s=21</a>"},{"pid":"c5738e40e41c222e9a8d970235f695140b26a3ec","tid":1523571,"uid":33930,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:57:17.000Z","msg":"一人一Post 洗爆連登時事台 Facebook<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n標題：［901入機場］今日重演721，黑警太子版核爆！唔使講野，入機場哂冷<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n與其死係街頭，不如死係機場<br />\n與其街頭食彈，不如機場食彈<br />\n與其被打爆頭，不如機場爆頭<br />\n與其被打爆眼，不如機場爆眼<br />\n與其黨鐵被打，不如機鐵被打<br />\n臥底鐘意燒街，不如燒機場啦<br />\n<br />\n攬炒機場！塞爆佢，唔使講野！<br />\n901無限期塞爆機場！<br />\n<br />\n見者Copy內容開新Post洗版，唔開Post自己檢討一下良心仲係唔係到！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sXnY1hQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsXnY1hQ.jpg&h=abafa30f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ea4a3edf3655a40540740e27d6335eceebf3492e","tid":1523571,"uid":48777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:58:27.000Z","msg":"自推1"},{"pid":"03816bdddcbf2b1e1505c032b982fa82b5666d46","tid":1523571,"uid":48777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:58:55.000Z","msg":"自推2"},{"pid":"d4d6e198baff8e47a84051da86796e1d5693c6b2","tid":1523571,"uid":48777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:59:05.000Z","msg":"自推3"},{"pid":"9457d052b9eb551e6f277d4f45b71731d2cc7385","tid":1523571,"uid":48777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:59:21.000Z","msg":"自推4"},{"pid":"3469d04cccfa295046e9744f1888746768b065c2","tid":1523571,"uid":48777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:59:32.000Z","msg":"自推5"},{"pid":"3255652df04804a192dc05fd91e619d799e2a06f","tid":1523571,"uid":104138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:59:35.000Z","msg":"係屋企睇緊live 又或者唔敢睇live既你都可以幫手!!<br />\n<br />\n係twitter簡單講幾句就已經得!<br />\ntwitter 要真實唔可以個個貼一樣既圖<br />\n上到twitter去#LIHKG, #StandwithHK, #HongKongProtestors 已經搵到大把料<br />\n只需要按retweet with comment，打返好簡短既個人感受就完成!!<br />\n人人都做到<br />\n可以既話可以係自己既tweet或者人地既tweet tag 其他地方既名人同官員都得!!<br />\n<br />\n只要夠多人，跟上面既方法就可以傳到唔同國家既記者，然後就會透過d 記者傳返去佢地既國家既人/報館最後就會到官員<br />\ntwitter既玩法好簡單，簡單retweet with comment 打返感受已經幫到好多!!"},{"pid":"fc11c9c3ef73c220b1646f0b3b828b2e453cd1e3","tid":1523571,"uid":253573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:59:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86c0ba54fc9c1c1628f2e0ac92613b8209731a4c","tid":1523571,"uid":166634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:59:46.000Z","msg":"呢條片少左頭幾秒毆打情侶既片